module REQ_ADMIN_LOG_01

/*
 * Alloy 6 ? Structural & Behavioral Model for Formal Verification
 * Requirement : REQ-ADMIN-LOG-01
 * Title       : Admin Actions Logging Requirement
 * Type        : Functional
 * Priority    : High
